BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:B7kQyzFlVBsRtEinjZ83c
SUMMARY:Letters Aloud: Love Me or Leave Me
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260214T193000Z
DESCRIPTION:Get ready to laugh\\\, swoon\\\, and maybe cringe just a little
	—Love Me or Leave Me from Letters Aloud unleashes the wild side of romance
	 in a whirlwind show packed with real letters from history’s most lovelorn
	 (and love-scorned) souls. With a cast of spirited actors\\\, comedy crack
	les from every confession\\\, break-up\\\, and “did-they-really-write-that
	?” misadventure\\\, all paired with lively music that sets hearts and funn
	y bones tingling. It’s an unfiltered anthology of grand gestures\\\, awkwa
	rd flirtations\\\, ridiculous rejections\\\, and letters so sincere (or sp
	ectacularly misguided) you can’t help but cheer. Whether you arrive hopele
	ssly romantic or deliciously cynical\\\, you’ll end the night loving every
	 memorable misstep on the bumpy road to happily ever after.\n\nFrom Town H
	all Seattle
URL:https://townhallseattle.org/event/letters-aloud-love-me-or-leave-me/
LOCATION:The Wyncote NW Forum\\\, 1119 8th Ave (Entrance off Seneca St.)\\\
	, Seattle\\\, 98101\\\, United States
TRANSP:TRANSPARENT
DURATION:PT
END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:PWSU2kxU5M5CoaxMsoNf3
SUMMARY:Comedy of Love: A Valentine’s Day Improv
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260214T200000Z
DESCRIPTION:Improvised comedy filled with passion\, lust\, heartbreak\, and
	 everything in between. Looking for a Valentine's Day plan that’s as unpre
	dictable as love itself? Don’t miss The Comedy of Love – a side-splitting\
	, heart-throbbing improv show that will have you laughing\, blushing\, and
	 maybe even swooning! Watch as real-life couples from our talented ensembl
	e turn your wild suggestions into unscripted tales of passion\, heartbreak
