UID:DHC7j0wBJzLEfMfSbAMSp
SUMMARY:DAY OF REMEMBRANCE 2026 - TOURS &amp\; RESOURCES
DTSTAMP:20260214T003616Z
DTSTART:20260221T180000Z
DESCRIPTION:The Day of Remembrance\, observed on February 19\, marks the an
	niversary of the signing of EO 9066\, which set into motion the incarcerat
	ion of Japanese Americans and their families during WWII. You can learn mo
	re about this historic breach of civil rights through a number of events t
	hroughout February\, March and April.\n\nFrom Wing Luke Museum
URL:https://www.wingluke.org/eventscalendar/2026-day-of-remembrance-beyond-
	the-barbed-wire
