DESCRIPTION:Want to ride a motorcycle but don’t know where to start? Join C
	ascade Motorcycle Safety and Ride With Us for a chance to experience ridin
	g a motorcycle for free\\\, with professional Cascade Motorcycle Safety Ri
	derCoaches helping you through each step. These 1-on-1\\\, 20-minute sessi
	ons are designed for total beginners\\\, with bikes and helmets provided. 
	\\nThis program is presented with the support of Vulcan Real Estate and Ca
	scade Motorcycle Safety. \\nRide out the remainder of the day in MOHAI to 
	see Kickstands Up! 125 Years of Motorcycling in the PNW. Program participa
	nts will receive a coupon for $5 off museum admission.\n\nFrom MOHAI - Mus
	eum of History & Industry
